za.co.neilson.sqlite.orm.annotations

Annotation Type Transient


  • @Target(value=FIELD)
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Transient
    Specifies that an object property should not be managed by the Object Model. A column in the database table will not be created for a field marked with the Transient annotation
    Since:
    0.1
    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    Sheldon Neilson
